com.apple.audio.hardware
Interface AStreamPropertyListener

public interface AStreamPropertyListener

This interface is implemented by applications to listen for property changes to an AudioStream

Method Summary
 int execute(AudioStream inStream, int inChannel, int inPropertyID)
          This call is called when an application has registered an object that implements this interface to receive notifications of changes in particular properties of an AudioStream.
 

Method Detail

execute

public int execute(AudioStream inStream,
                   int inChannel,
                   int inPropertyID)
This call is called when an application has registered an object that implements this interface to receive notifications of changes in particular properties of an AudioStream.

Parameters:
inStream - the stream that has had a property change
inChannel - the channel of the stream that has changed
inPropertyID - the propertyID that identifies what has changed on the supplied stream and channel
Returns:
zero if no error
